title: Website reports on news as if Hillary Clinton won election
text: Indenial.com: Website allows Hillary Clinton supporters to pretend to live in alternate universe where the Democratic candidate won HillarybeatTrump.org brands itself as 'News from the real America where the majority rules' The site publishes fake news about a world in where Clinton is the 45th president Articles report on Hillary's approval rates rising to '89 per cent' Other headlines include: 'Clinton raises taxes, Koch brothers flee America' The site states the views are satirical, but also calls itself a 'movement' Published: 21:23 GMT, 23 February 2017 | Updated: 23:45 GMT, 23 February 2017 70 shares
